#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Dupahiya Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents 
Dupahiya Official Trailer  
Starring Gajraj Rao, Sparsh Shrivastava, Renuka Shahane, Bhuvan Arora, Shivani Raghuvanshi, Yashpal Sharma, Komal Kushwaha 
Written by Chirag Garg, Avinash Dwivedi 
Directed by Sonam Nair 
Creators and Executive Producers - Salona Bains Joshi and Shubh Shivdasani
Production House - Bombay Film Cartel
 
Official Release Date Mar 7, 2025 on Prime Video India. 
 
About: 
Dhadakpur is the Belgium of Bihar. Clean, green and glorious. And this year the village will celebrate its Silver Jubilee of being crime- free! And as a gift for the villagers there will be a trophy, clean water but most of all pride. 
Also within 8 days, Roshni, the prettiest girl of the village will leave the Jha family and be wedded to Kuber. The plan was to marry his elder brother Durlabh, but the moment she heard that Durlabh‚Äôs younger brother works in Mumbai she didn‚Äôt even bat an eyelid to change the groom. Like her friends, Roshni too aspired for a modern city life.Her brother, Bhugol too has dreams of going to Mumbai and becoming a Bollywood superstar. 
 
The to-be-groom‚Äôs father is a clerk in the education department and Roshni‚Äôs dad, Banwari, is a temporary primary school teacher. This marriage meant his dream of a permanent job could be fulfilled. In short, everyone‚Äôs dreams hinge on this one wedding. But before their dreams could turn into reality, it was time to fulfill the to-be groom's dream. He wants a two-wheeler as a ‚Äúwedding gift‚Äù. But not just any two-wheeler. A shiny red expensive motorbike! That too with a year‚Äôs supply of petrol. No one in Dhadakpur had paid such a handsome dowry before-but the Jha family is determined. 

The bike arrives in the day and disaster strikes at night. It got stolen! How? When? Who? There were only questions and no answers. Dhadakpur is crime-free after all! 
Leading the queue of suspects, was Roshni‚Äôs, ex-boyfriend, Amavas. Years ago, he was banished from Dhadakpur for his incessant stealing. 
Pushpalata Yadav, is Dhadakpur‚Äôs village head. It was her idea to banish Amavas from the village, but now he was their only hope. He could procure a second hand bike. 
Bhugol and Amavas are then sent to get the bike. Two childhood enemies. Chalk and cheese. Coffee and sleep. Ronaldo and The World Cup. How the two boys save the pride of the village and ensure the wedding happens as planned forms the crux of the season. 

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started from February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. After the victory against Bangladesh, Team India also won against Pakistan by 6 wickets. While there is a wave of happiness among Indian cricket fans, Pakistani cricket fans are afraid that Pakistan is almost out of the Champions Trophy. How excited are Pakistani fans for the India vs Pakistan match? Virat Kohli became the hero of victory for India who scored a brilliant century. Why did the fans of the Pakistan cricket team become admirers of the Indian cricket team? Why did the Pakistan cricket fans get angry at the star players of the Pakistani team Babar Azam, Haris Rauf, Shaheen Afridi, Mohammad Rizwan? Why did the much-discussed Pakistani bowling fail in front of Shubman Gill, Shreyas Iyer, Virat, Rohit Sharma? What happened when after the India vs Pakistan match in Dubai, Indian cricket fans and Pakistani cricket fans together trolled and roasted the Pakistan cricket team. To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch.

How excited are Pakistani fans for the India vs Pakistan match? Virat Kohli became the hero of victory for India who scored a brilliant century. Why did the fans of the Pakistan cricket team become admirers of the Indian cricket team? What happened when after the India vs Pakistan match in Dubai, Indian cricket fans and Pakistani cricket fans together trolled and roasted the Pakistan cricket team. Why did the fans of the Pakistan cricket team become admirers of the Indian cricket team? Why did the Pakistan cricket fans get angry at the star players of the Pakistani team Babar Azam, Haris Rauf, Shaheen Afridi, Mohammad Rizwan? Why did the much-discussed Pakistani bowling fail in front of Shubman Gill, Shreyas Iyer, Virat, Rohit Sharma? What happened when after the India vs Pakistan match in Dubai, Indian cricket fans and Pakistani cricket fans together trolled and roasted the Pakistan cricket team. To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4329 - Bhide ke Jaal me Phase Mahagyani Baba?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Bhide Bana Detactive | Bhide Ka Naya Mission | 

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

en-IN.description:
Bhide Bana Detactive | Bhide Ka Naya Mission |

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: When You Have a Crush On Your Boss - Part 2| Ft. Keshav Sadhna,  Anjum Khan, Reshham Sahaani
snippet.description:
#filtercopy #officeromace #crush

Kaisa laga Part 2? Comments mein batao üòã

Ever felt that sudden wave of... something... when your boss is around? We're diving into that feeling! Yeah, we've all been there! In this super fun video, we're diving straight into the hilarious mess of having a crush on your boss! üòÖ

We've packed it with all the relatable moments of office romance, the kind where you're constantly wondering, "Is this real, or am I just imagining things?" ü§∑‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è From accidental touches during team meetings to trying to decipher those "friendly" smiles that might mean something more, every moment is a minefield of mixed signals.You know that feeling when you're trying to act cool, but your heart is doing a bhangra inside? 

This video is for anyone who's ever had a crush on their boss, found themselves overthinking every little interaction, or just loves a good dose of desi comedy. Get ready for some serious LOL moments, a few cringes (because, let's be honest, we've all been there!), and a whole lot of "OMG, same!" vibes.

So settle in, and get ready to dive into the chaos of office romance. Don't forget to LIKE, COMMENT, and SUBSCRIBE for more hilarious content! And share your own office crush stories in the comments ‚Äì we want to hear all the juicy details! üòâ Let's see if your office crush stories are as crazy as ours!

Don't forget to follow us for more fun content!

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/filtercopy
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FilterCopy/

en.title: When You Have a Crush On Your Boss - Part 2| Ft. Keshav Sadhna,  Anjum Khan, Reshham Sahaani
en.description:
#filtercopy #officeromace #crush

Kaisa laga Part 2? Comments mein batao üòã

Ever felt that sudden wave of... something... when your boss is around? We're diving into that feeling! Yeah, we've all been there! In this super fun video, we're diving straight into the hilarious mess of having a crush on your boss! üòÖ

We've packed it with all the relatable moments of office romance, the kind where you're constantly wondering, "Is this real, or am I just imagining things?" ü§∑‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è From accidental touches during team meetings to trying to decipher those "friendly" smiles that might mean something more, every moment is a minefield of mixed signals.You know that feeling when you're trying to act cool, but your heart is doing a bhangra inside? 

This video is for anyone who's ever had a crush on their boss, found themselves overthinking every little interaction, or just loves a good dose of desi comedy. Get ready for some serious LOL moments, a few cringes (because, let's be honest, we've all been there!), and a whole lot of "OMG, same!" vibes.

So settle in, and get ready to dive into the chaos of office romance. Don't forget to LIKE, COMMENT, and SUBSCRIBE for more hilarious content! And share your own office crush stories in the comments ‚Äì we want to hear all the juicy details! üòâ Let's see if your office crush stories are as crazy as ours!

Mann Mast Malang Episode 03 - [Eng Sub] - Danish Taimoor - Sahar Hashmi - 23rd February 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fianc√©s turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Real Madrid 3-1 Man City | Mbappe (3) & Nico Goals
snippet.description:
Manchester City were knocked out this season‚Äôs UEFA Champions League after a 6-3 aggregate defeat to Real Madrid.
Pep Guardiola‚Äôs side were beaten 3-1 in the second leg at the Santiago Bernabeu with Kylian Mbappe scoring a hat-trick for the current European champions.

After a 3-2 defeat in the first leg at the Etihad, City fell further behind in the tie when the Frenchman scored the opener after just four minutes.

And we suffered a further early early setback with John Stones going off injured after just eight minutes while Erling Haaland was unable to feature in the fixture.

Mbappe scored two more either side of half-time before Nico scored his first goal for City in the dying minutes.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4328 - Bhide ka Mission Kauwa Kaate?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri
